## Background

[{{ meta.title }}]({{ repository.url }}) is a command-line tool for converting text in English to [title case](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Title_case). It was born out of frustration with the speed of a previous implementation in JavaScript which shall remain unreleased out of shame and a desire to ~~procrastinate~~ learn some Rust.

## Usage

```
USAGE:
    tcc <text>...

FLAGS:
    -h, --help       Prints help information
    -V, --version    Prints version information

ARGS:
    <text>...    The text to convert to title case.
```

